This is the readme file for User Board extension and is compatible with MediaWiki 1.39.

==Intro==
User Board extension provides for user-to-user modern thread style messages into your MediaWiki. 

==Usage==
Currently in order to send a message, append the following to url: `index.php?title=Special:UserBoard&user=USERNAME`
USERNAME is the user you wish to message.

==Authors==
User Board was extracted from SocialProfile in December 2022 by Amazing Wikis Org 

